sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Application
    participant libpq as libpq (fe-exec.c)
    participant PG as Postgres (copyto.c)

    Note over App, PG: Initial Command Phase
    App->>libpq: PQexec("COPY table TO STDOUT")
    libpq->>PG: Query(COPY TO...)
    PG->>PG: 1. Query source relation
    PG-->>libpq: PGRES_COPY_OUT (Ready to send)
    libpq-->>App: Return PGresult

    Note over App, PG: Streaming Phase (COPY State)
    loop until server finishes
        App->>libpq: PQgetCopyData()
        libpq->>PG: Request next chunk
        PG->>PG: 2. Convert tuples to format
        PG->>PG: 3. Serialize to COPY messages
        PG-->>libpq: CopyData chunk
        libpq-->>App: Return buffer
    end

    Note over App, PG: Termination Phase
    PG-->>libpq: CommandComplete
    App->>libpq: PQgetResult()
    libpq-->>App: Final PGresult (Success)
